<h2>What is Canvas?</h2>

<p>The HTML5 <strong>&lt;canvas&gt;</strong> element is used to draw graphics, on the fly, via scripting (usually JavaScript).</p>

<p>The <strong>&lt;canvas&gt;</strong> element is only a container for graphics. You must use a script to actually draw the graphics.</p>

<p>Canvas has several methods for drawing paths, boxes, circles, characters, and adding images.</p>